{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/fast_escape_burning_city.gif?t=1734605296\" /><i><strong>Tiny Hero Courier</strong> is a fast-paced action game set in a miniature <strong>tilt-shift</strong> world! Play as Rupert, a courier in a post-apocalyptic world, <strong>delivering packages</strong> while dodging zombies, solving puzzles, and navigating dynamic, visually stunning diorama-like environments.<br><br><strong>Tiny Hero Courier</strong> is inspired by miniature worlds, dioramas, and the <strong>&quot;Love, Death &amp; Robots&quot;</strong> episode <strong>&quot;Night of the Mini Dead.&quot;</strong> The game humorously portrays Rupert\u2019s adventures, showing how an ordinary courier\u2019s life can turn extraordinary as he becomes a true hero.</i><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/Dynamic_Package_Delivery_System_Bar_v1.png?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/lab_and_metro_delivery.gif?t=1734605296\" /><strong>Deliver packages of various sizes</strong>, each affecting movement speed and strategy. Special packages, like explosive <strong>TNT</strong> or <strong>fragile items</strong>, add unique gameplay challenges and require careful handling to avoid failure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/rupert_bombs_cemetery_gasstation.gif?t=1734605296\" />Players must <strong>hold a button</strong> to carry packages, creating tension and adding an extra layer of skill to the delivery process. <strong>Dropping a package</strong> comes with consequences, making each delivery feel impactful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/Interactive_Mechanics_Bar.png?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/electric_traps_and_propellers.gif?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rupert</strong> uses <strong>switches</strong> and <strong>mechanisms</strong> to solve puzzles, <strong>activate traps</strong>, and clear obstacles along his path. Every interaction brings him closer to completing his deliveries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/Boss_encounters_Bar.png?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/miniboss_battle_mall_cave.gif?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players must carefully navigate and strategize to face or avoid <strong>powerful bosses</strong> and <strong>minibosses</strong>. One wrong move can trigger dangerous foes, testing your reflexes and tactical skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/Explorable_World_Map_Bar.png?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/map_mission_zombie_smash.gif?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Navigate an interactive <strong>world map</strong> where players can drive Rupert\u2019s vehicle to explore new areas, <strong>unlock missions</strong>, and discover secrets. The map is inspired by a similar system seen in <strong>Cuphead</strong> game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/Multifunctional_Device_Bar.png?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/rupert_calls_boss.gif?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Access the map, <strong>upgrade your vehicle</strong>, and make crucial calls to characters like your <strong>boss</strong>. This <strong>handy device</strong> is your all-in-one tool for survival and <strong>strategic planning</strong> in the post-apocalyptic world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/Humor_and_absurd_locations_Bar.png?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/death_in_subway_cemetery_lab.gif?t=1734605296\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Watch your step!</strong> Rupert\u2019s journey is full of danger, where one wrong move can lead to death. From delivering packages to the devil in <strong>hell</strong> to surviving bizarre, post-apocalyptic landscapes, every location offers unexpected challenges with a touch of <strong>humor</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/extras/rupert_in_hell.png?t=1734605296\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734605296","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734605296","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408450/5f3beb186427e8a2c46ddb199b99fadc080dcd2d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734605296","capsule_ima